---
title: Za'atar and Feta Tart with Spinach Salad and Sliced Almonds
description: There’s nothing like a free-form tart to make you feel a bit fancy at dinnertime. This colourful beauty is all about the tender ribbons of zucchini, the sweetness of roasted shallots and the salty finish of feta. It’s unbeatable!
